Date: Tue, 19 Nov 2019 10:09:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2174/4530] drm/i915/gem: Protect the obj->vma.list during
 iteration

Take the obj->vma.lock to prevent modifications to the list as we
iterate, to avoid the dreaded NULL pointer.

